"i would really appreciate just something going in" jmc@@
@
text
@d1 1
a1 1
.\"	$OpenBSD: malo.4,v 1.26 2008/07/27 13:02:38 mglocker Exp $
d29 1
a29 1
.Dd $Mdocdate: July 27 2008 $
d78 8
